We loved the clean spacious rooms, comfortable bed, decor, lighting, free use of safe in the room and air con and the rooftop terrace with pool and jacuzzi.	I felt the hotel info book was a little on the lean side and the elecronic room safe kept locking itself with our money and passports inside!	Felt very safe in the area, as a single woman with two children in tow.	The room was clean and comfortable with a free room safe which was a welcome find.	Area is nice, safe with great shops ect, is about 15-20 min walk to La Ramblas and good location for metro stations.